---
title: Spicy Curried Chicken Breast Stew with Garlic Flatbread
description: Is there anything better than a big bowl of warm chicken curry? It's a hug from the inside out! Tender chicken, aromatic curry spices and roasted sweet potatoes fill the bowl to the brim. Don't forget to wipe it clean with the garlic flatbread!
